title: On Camera, Suicide Bomber Blows Herself Up In Karachi, 3 Chinese Killed - NDTV
content: On Camera, Suicide Bomber Blows Herself Up In Karachi, 3 Chinese Killed  NDTVView Full coverage on Google News
description: A woman suicide bomber from a Pakistan separatist group killed four people, including three Chinese nationals, in an attack on a vehicle carrying staff from the Confucious Institute affiliated with the Karachi University.
